# ADR-004: Pre-stage Workflow Templates and Support Multi-Account Onboarding

## Status
Accepted

## Context
OpenOps workflows need to be reusable and support onboarding multiple customer AWS accounts.

## Decision
- Store workflow templates as JSON files in the repository and ECS container.
- Enhance OpenOps to support IAM role-based onboarding for multiple customer accounts.

## Consequences
- Faster onboarding for new customers.
- Consistent workflow automation across environments.

## Date
2025-07-11